"  Crust:","2 1/4 cups all-purpose flour, divided","3/4 cup (3 ounces) extra-sharp cheddar cheese, shredded","1/2 cup ice water","1/2 teaspoon salt","1/4 cup chilled butter, cut into small pieces","  Filling:","10 cup very thinly sliced peeled Granny Smith apple (about 2 3/4 pounds)","2 tablespoons fresh lemon juice","1/3 cup packed brown sugar","1/4 cup granulated sugar","1/4 teaspoon ground cinnamon","1/4 teaspoon ground nutmeg","1/4 teaspoon ground ginger","  Dash of salt","  Cooking spray","1  large egg white, lightly beaten"